column2: select ID, Vintage, Tract     , log1#mi=log1#(#*geom.EnvelopeAngle())     , lon=centroid.Long, lat=centroid.Lat     , wkt=geom.STIntersection(@area).ToString()     , dist2center=geom.STDistance(@center) from optw.tamass.TRACTS  where vintage = #     and geom.STArea() < #e9 -- m^# -- excluding only one huge tract     and geom.STDistance(@center) < # / # * # -- meters
